         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596"><!-- p1l1-r30 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e108">Rubrica 30</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De peccato et peccatoribus consideratione religiosa</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
      ¶ De peccato et peccatoribus conside
      <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>ratione religiosa. Rubrica 30
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>PSalmista. i pslamus <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e125">Bea
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>tus vir qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>non abiit in consilio impiorum: et in via pec <!--49.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>catorum non stetit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e139"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e141"> psalmus. 10. Qui diligit iniquita
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>tem odit animam suam. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e148"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e150"> 36 psalmus Considerat peccator
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>iustum et querit mortificare eum: dominus autem non de
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>relinquet eum in manibus eius. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e162">¶ Salomodo in prouer. c. 23. Ne emuletur cor
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>tuum peccatores: sed in timore dei estote tota die:
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>quia habebis spem in nouissimo: et presto
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>latio tua non auferetur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e176">¶ Thobie hysto. c. 12. Qui faciunt peccata et
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>iniquitatem: hostes sunt animae sue. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e186">¶ Iesus fi. sirach in eccl. ca. 5. Non adijcias
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>peccatum: et ne dicas miseratio dei magna est: mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>tudi peccatorum meorum miserebitur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e194"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e196"> c. 9. Non ze
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>les gloriam et opes peccatoris: non enim scis quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>futura sit illius subuersio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e208">¶ Mattheus in euan. c. 19 Iesus dixit: Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>homicidium facies: non adult erabis: non facies
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>furtum: non falsum testimonium dices. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e221">¶ Ioannes in epistula. c. i. Si dixerimus quoniam peccatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>non habemus: ipsi nos seducimus: et veritas
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>in nobis non est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e229"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e231"> ca. 8. Omnis qui facit peccatum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>seruus peccati est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e237"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e239"> c. 9. Si ceci essetis: non
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>haberetis peccatum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e245"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e247"> Idem epi i. c. 3. Omnis quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>facit peccatum et iniquitatem facit: et peccatum est ini
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>quitas. Qui facit peccatum ex diabolo est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e255"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e257"> c. 5.
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>et fi. Omnis iniquitas peccatum est: et est peccatum ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>mortem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e265"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e267"> Idem epistola. 2. c. vnico. Qui male
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>facit non videt deum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e278">¶ Iudas alphei apostolus: qui fuit frater iacobi
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>apostoli epistola vnica. cap. 2. et fi. Peccatores
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>impii hi sunt: murmuratores: querulosi secundum
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>desideria sua ambulantes: et os illorum loqui
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>tur superbiam: mirantes personas questus causa. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e290">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e294">¶ Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. i. Peccatum cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>consummatum fuerit generat mortem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e300"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e302"> c. 4. Sed
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>enti bonum facere et non facienti peccatum est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e312">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. i. ad corinthios. ca. 10
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Non potestis mense dei participes esse et
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>mense demoniorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e320"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e322"> c. 15. Stimulus mor
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>tis peccatum est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e328">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e332">¶ Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: libro 17 epistola
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>et. Omnibus crimen suum voluptati est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e339">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e343">/ Idem de moribus. Omne peccatum actio
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>est voluntaria. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e349">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e353">¶ Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 9. Sepe occa <!--50.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="12-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>sio peccandi voluntatem facit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e365">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e369">¶ Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria: par
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>ticula. i. c. 6. Peccatum geminat peccantis
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>gloria: culpam. Diffamat fame dissipentis ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>nor. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e379"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e381"> c. 12. Uenialis est peccandi inciden
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>tia: sed criminalis peccandi frequentia. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
